{"tid":1413842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"由幾時開始民意變得唔重要?","createTime":"2019-08-05T11:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T02:08:36.000Z","uid":76813,"like":71,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b136626078a2eba19caddc9f3f71a1efbd6c449f","tid":1413842,"uid":76813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:04:29.000Z","msg":"近期唔知係咪有三毛帶風向<br />\n當有巴打俾意見，希望為運動爭取更多支持既時侯，就會有一班人出黎屌<br />\n理由如下:<br />\n1. 冷氣軍師收皮，落場先講<br />\n攬炒巴，搵仔tg group admin，陶傑李怡呢班都無落場<br />\n大家都係各自各盡做，不分化唔係一個口號，係要實踐<br />\n2. 已經唔需要民意，69, 616證明民意無用，612證明只有行動最實際<br />\n我仲見到有民意撚呢個term出現...<br />\n<br />\n無錯，行動係必須，612無各位挺身而出，法例可能已經通過<br />\n但係，都希望大家理解: 民意係最大既盾牌<br />\n我明白勇武派可能感受唔到呢一點，因為你地長期面對警察，無時無刻承受人身以至法律風險，唔覺得有民意幫助緊<br />\n或者你地諗下物資組，黃大仙、將軍澳街坊，參與罷工既各位打工仔<br />\n佢地為數不少屬於溫和派: 唔衝唔企前線，但係佢地都會有意見想表達<br />\n所謂既民意，其實就包括左呢班人既支持<br />\n明白前線各位既憤怒，但都停一停諗一諗天琦信中呢句: 政治係爭取唔同意自己既人既支持<br />\n<br />\n結論:<br />\n1.爭取民意<br />\n民意絕對係要爭取，而且更加係長期爭取目標<br />\n佔中既失敗其中主因就係民意消散<br />\n我唔反對不合作運動，同埋針對警察既各樣行動<br />\n但大家要保持底線：唔針對一般市民，唔好連鬧你幾句都開佢拖(咁做同犬何異?)<br />\n同埋做好文宣：唔好見人就屌，我明白你地會好躁，躁就將面對市民既工作交比和理非<br />\n<br />\n2.唔好灰心，請準備長期抗爭，有牌可打<br />\n大家請明白對手唔係一個民選政府，更加唔係香港政府呢個弱勢政府<br />\n一路以黎對手只有一個：中國共產黨<br />\n呢個黨有幾硬淨(至少表面取態上)，大家心知肚明<br />\n兩個月五大訴求無一滿足係令人沮喪<br />\n但係大家唔好灰心，同呢個大boss對奕，需要有長期抗爭既準備<br />\n係呢個局勢入面，我地唔係無牌可打：<br />\n香港依然無可替代<br />\n中國有6成ipo係香港，過半舉債係香港，成個利益集團呢十幾年黎買落無數香港資產<br />\n若非如此，以佢地唔怕俾人制裁既強人性格，一早落order搞掂香港<br />\n中共內外交迫<br />\n中美貿戰，中國地區政府負債加劇<br />\n中共如果有心，應盡快搞掂香港，方便走資<br />\n<br />\n大家加油"},{"pid":"7e025ac2ac9df41add325b24bcc94f6fb3093267","tid":1413842,"uid":76813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:27:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fdd8231c1c91f4e526990075735f7c7caed35e6e","tid":1413842,"uid":229886,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:31:07.000Z","msg":"今日見到前線屌市民就火都黎<br />\n利申前線"},{"pid":"dcd44e6e300f6f14ac24e8dcb7320910797b92ef","tid":1413842,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"今日大罷工集會，<br />\n只計金鐘人數都近六四集會，<br />\n如果你問逆轉未，<br />\n我好肯定答你，未"},{"pid":"9116bc229545087d379382c190d1016aa9400c41","tid":1413842,"uid":76813,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"dcd44e6e300f6f14ac24e8dcb7320910797b92ef","tid":1413842,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"今日大罷工集會，<br />\n只計金鐘人數都近六四集會，<br />\n如果你問逆轉未，<br />\n我好肯定答你，未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:38:20.000Z","msg":"我係出黎既其中一個<br />\n但係我相信唔少人同我一樣都有憂慮<br />\n依家未唔代表將來唔會<br />\n希望大家一言一行都係增加緊我方既力量，而唔係相反<br />\n<br />\n有d巴打一開波就屌(無論係現實定連登)，我真心唔認同"},{"pid":"a0ef655dc60ad425da088ac86d97aba4bab85949","tid":1413842,"uid":259901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:45:27.000Z","msg":"真係，明大家好大壓力，但真係唔好變成你敵人咁樣"},{"pid":"69b0e7f98415cda43dbb7c0b0b1b7083551b663a","tid":1413842,"uid":136971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6adb790e2bb54d117010724876fb357d8bd74647","tid":1413842,"uid":52090,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9116bc229545087d379382c190d1016aa9400c41","tid":1413842,"uid":76813,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"dcd44e6e300f6f14ac24e8dcb7320910797b92ef","tid":1413842,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"今日大罷工集會，<br />\n只計金鐘人數都近六四集會，<br />\n如果你問逆轉未，<br />\n我好肯定答你，未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:38:20.000Z","msg":"我係出黎既其中一個<br />\n但係我相信唔少人同我一樣都有憂慮<br />\n依家未唔代表將來唔會<br />\n希望大家一言一行都係增加緊我方既力量，而唔係相反<br />\n<br />\n有d巴打一開波就屌(無論係現實定連登)，我真心唔認同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:54:34.000Z","msg":"呢點我同意，<br />\n有件事本來想開post講<br />\n<br />\n有一次，<br />\n有一班巴打絲打係橋下行，<br />\n<br />\n橋上有個藍屍，<br />\n一睇就知係廢老嘅人講「臭雞」，「仆街仔」，等大量粗口<br />\n<br />\n巴打絲打當然還口，叫佢落黎，<br />\n個廢老就叫人上去<br />\n<br />\n有位巴打衝上去，廢老當場嚇親，<br />\n衝到一半，有好多同伴大叫「我地係大學生，唔係毅進仔，番黎啊」<br />\n個巴打就停一停，諗一諗就番轉頭繼續行<br />\n<br />\n各位，老實講，出左黎兩個月，<br />\n有巴打絲打情緒差係肯定，<br />\n但希望同行人，可以係佢地做錯事之前，<br />\n擋一擋，等佢地可以停一停，諗一諗<br />\n你地需要佢嘅勇敢，但佢都需要你地嘅理性"},{"pid":"ed0886f936a597553729350af0311b5808e9de52","tid":1413842,"uid":182978,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:54:44.000Z","msg":"屌，好同意，唔理民意嘅話，我地同個垃圾政府有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n天琦：「政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。」"},{"pid":"07365fca9426902c3e2ccd5fe184026c4aa6940f","tid":1413842,"uid":217080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:55:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6ecf741fd2f6a57dc4184df304df95020f7a7c21","tid":1413842,"uid":292053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c059deb009cec20e82798127bb32f8c39e7127fb","tid":1413842,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:07:57.000Z","msg":"見到街坊個個diu狗，仲需要care民意？已經好明顯啦唔係咩？"},{"pid":"9c5de37b4230c71e2e0bc8af60acda024424856f","tid":1413842,"uid":240296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ed0886f936a597553729350af0311b5808e9de52","tid":1413842,"uid":182978,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:54:44.000Z","msg":"屌，好同意，唔理民意嘅話，我地同個垃圾政府有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n天琦：「政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:10:51.000Z","msg":"可惜好多人選擇圍爐取暖，唔岩聽就block 人，冇盡力去解釋問題所在"},{"pid":"b23d4eabb6df838c7ef8e10ab9d67a88376a675d","tid":1413842,"uid":268410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:14:27.000Z","msg":"已經冇底線"},{"pid":"598b41da3a7f991cee6f86e5a446c0e76016bf04","tid":1413842,"uid":281418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:15:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5b480468a5f08b74e20aa9bb14c39235030e7239","tid":1413842,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:16:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"24560c7c618ba770ad5b9d46aa13508a06ddf274","tid":1413842,"uid":46578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:17:03.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n民意其實係我地而家最大嘅本錢<br />\n之前好多行動都係牽動緊民心"},{"pid":"0d8ccb5f5dc499f92a2c140726c83fab47f21eb5","tid":1413842,"uid":172477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:19:42.000Z","msg":"天琦専登寫封信俾大家，<br />\n叫大家唔好俾仇恨蓋過理智，<br />\n叫大家爭取對家支持。<br />\n但好似無人記得咁。<br />\n<br />\n希望有時候可以重睇一次，<br />\n理解下佢嘅意思。"},{"pid":"e076c5c8890c1533fbeff2ffbc2e167cbaca262b","tid":1413842,"uid":199617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"民意可能逼唔到政府做嘢，但冇民意場運動就會散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以文宣要繼續做；另外前線勇武嘅手足希望您會忍一忍，唔好畀情緒主導咗您嘅行動，抗爭最需要理性。公關嘅嘢做咗好過唔做，仲有行動前要三思，今日有單放嘢上路軌好危險㗎，下次記住塞鐵就可以喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"78147ad3a96694a2e9440e2e70461cb18f5c88c7","tid":1413842,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:24:30.000Z","msg":"各有各做<br />\n勇武嘅手足喺前線搏埋條命<br />\n和你飛可以做嘅 就係諗辦法幫佢哋贏民意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939e822e9425952f6695b728f89cb9dcf2b456c4","tid":1413842,"uid":18728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:25:01.000Z","msg":"以下目標為本，不討論道德：<br />\n<br />\n如果我地有高於警察/中共嘅武裝力量，可以不理民意，直接武裝政變奪權<br />\n<br />\n但我地無，所以民意係必需<br />\n呢度唔係指要去爭取我地屋企深藍兩老嘅民意（可以試，但實在太難），而係防止二百萬和理非/淺黃民意流失<br />\n無咗呢班人，勇武手足被拉被殺唔夠人理，亦唔夠人捐錢俾義士打官司<br />\n以現時我地資源，團結係最大力量，亦係中共最唔想見到"},{"pid":"1fba7c7cb525e9bfb4d748913cd8f1162a63f106","tid":1413842,"uid":76813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:09:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e8d75f4dfd32445212e7de93acea3f62f1fa5a0f","tid":1413842,"uid":203813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:27:00.000Z","msg":"重要post push"},{"pid":"86ccb2d1a509019cb81db1ae63c40cb1c6dfbe3c","tid":1413842,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57bb265e0c03f22fa401647eb14d2a30f2b69081","tid":1413842,"uid":196115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:29:51.000Z","msg":"保持克制<br />\n除咗對狗同鬼"}]}